A hungry blade that devours the life of its user to grant them strength.

LEGENDARY: Portal Dive - Create an umbral explosion and teleport high into the air. Reactivate to crash down, creating another umbral explosion on impact.
SPECIAL: Feast - When meter is full, activate. While active, you continuously lose health, but you have lifesteal, continuously generate Valour, and launch umbral slashes ahead of you with each attack.
PASSIVE: Verge of Night - You have 2 held MIGHT.

The Hunger Gameplay Weapon (Sword - Umbral) x1

A spiked club that handles with the finesse of a sword. The wielder stands their ground against Behemoths, while dealing crushing damage to stagger them.

LEGENDARY: Thunderous Charge - Become lightning, finding the nearest Behemoth and teleporting to it with an explosive shock burst.
SPECIAL: Avenging Overdrive - When meter is full, activate to gain 2 stacks of SPEED and take a brief defensive stance which will parry an incoming attack and counter it, entering overdrive. Reactivate during overdrive to parry again. Successful parries generate 1 Valour.
PASSIVE: Energetic - After a dodging through a Behemoth's attack, your next attacks generate 100% bonus meter.

Thundersoul Gameplay Weapon (Sword - Shock) x1

The Godhand refracts light through its prismatic design, focusing it into an intensely powerful beam of Radiant energy.

LEGENDARY: Gathering Power - Stand your ground, powering up and instantly filling your meter to full.
SPECIAL: Godhand - Convert your meter into ammo. Spend that ammo to channel a beam of radiant energy that deals increasing damage over time the longer it focuses on one part.
PASSIVE: Runic Sigils - When you activate your legendary, create a sigil on the ground that activates when a Behemoth crosses it, granting 250 shield.

The Godhand Gameplay Weapon (War Pike - Radiant) x1

Infused with blaze aether, Molten Edict ignites Behemoths with molten rock, before forming a pair of powerful gauntlets to pummel the burning foes into the ground.

LEGENDARY: Fist of the Mountain - Coat your fists in molten earth, changing your moveset. Your punches deal large amounts of blaze buildup, and your attacks deal increased damage against Behemoths who are on fire.
SPECIAL: Molten Orb - Lob balls of fire that deal increased damage and can set the ground on fire when charged with more ammo. Your Aetherslam unleashes a rolling ball of lava.
PASSIVE: Burning Earth - After spending 75 stamina, your next attack that hits a Behemoth launches a cone of flame.

Molten Edict Gameplay Weapon (Hammer - Blaze) x1

On the cusp of reality between the Shattered Isles and the Umbral realm ruled by by the Behemoth Thrax, lies the Reapers Edge. Dragging its wielder across the barrier to unleash punishing attacks against helpless Behemoths, stealing aether to empower themselves and allies.

LEGENDARY: Planar Rip - Rip a tear in the fabric of reality and enter the Umbral realm. While in it, take reduced damage, and become immune to stagger. For every 3000 damage dealt during it, give 1 MIGHT to friendly Slayers when it ends.
SPECIAL: Reaper's Flight - Throw Reapers Edge. It deals continuous damage over time while in flight, and then returns to you. Reactivate while in flight to teleport to its current position and perform an umbral strike in the direction your Slayer is facing.
PASSIVE: Umbral Corruption - Attacks have a chance to generate an umbral orb. Each orb increases the damage dealt by attacks by 1.75%. With 5 or more active orbs, the damage bonus per orb is doubled.

Reapers Edge Gameplay Weapon (Axe - Umbral) x1

With the inevitability of a glacier's movement, Eternal Winter crashes upon its enemies with incredible power. Slow, steady, and unstoppable.

LEGENDARY: Determined Strike - Perform a powerful strike. The strength of this attack is greatly increased based on your Determination Level.
SPECIAL: Grim Onslaught - Throw your axe. It deals a great deal of damage and bounces back. Catching it grants determination.
PASSIVE: Frozen Brand - Dealing damage to a Behemoth places a freezing brand on it. After a time, the brand will detonate. Dealing enough damage to the brand detonates it early, dealing increased damage. Recharges after a short time.

Eternal Winter Gameplay Weapon (Axe - Frost) x1

Dripping with a poison concoction that disrupts the aether of Behemoths, these Alchemical chain blades hasten their end, while drawing on terra aether to buff and heal their allies.

LEGENDARY: Bloom of Balm - Revive all allies in bleed out, and place a heal over time on all allies. Can be activated while in bleed out.
SPECIAL: Insatiable Dance - Push off a Behemoth and into the air. Activate a heavy attack while in the air to slam down, spending one or more chain charges to deal damage, heal yourself, and create orbs that heal allies.
PASSIVE: Dripping Venom - When you deal damage, deal 10% of the damage again over the next 5 seconds.

Bane & Balm Gameplay Weapon (Chain Blades - Terra) x1

As fleeting and beautiful as a snowflake, To & Fro flickers across the battlefield with the crisp edge of sharpened Vylmark steel, with an aura of speed and the sharpened bite of of winter.

LEGENDARY: Frigid Zeal - Activate an aura that grants all Slayers within it 3 held stacks of speed.
SPECIAL: Reaper's Dance - Push off a Behemoth and into the air. Activate a heavy attack to slam down, dealing damage based on the number of chain charges spent.
PASSIVE: Frost Sprites - On landing Reaper's Dance, spawn 3 frost sprites that cause your next attack to deal increased damage.

To & Fro Gameplay Weapon (Chain Blades - Frost) x1

A feat of Ostian Engineering, Firestorm launches Slayers into battle to unleash a wall of missiles and rain fire from an airship in the skies.

LEGENDARY: Airship Barrage - Dealing wound damage over the next 30 seconds builds up a reserve of cannon balls, which are then fired down on the nearest Behemoth from an airship above.
SPECIAL: Reckless Leap - Convert your meter into ammo. Spend that ammo to perform a flying lunge attack that deals up to 1500 damage based on distance and ammo quality.
PASSIVE: Homing Missiles - Your attacks can lock onto Behemoth parts. Dealing damage loads up homing missiles, that fire on the locked on part when you dodge.

Firestorm Gameplay Weapon (War Pike - Blaze) x1

A block of ever-frozen ice once used by a renowned Skaldish smith, The Anvil creates constructs of ice to aid your allies and turn the battlefield against Behemoths.

LEGENDARY: The Wall - Create a wall of ice that blocks projectiles, interrupts Behemoths that pass through it, and freezes non-frost Behemoths.
SPECIAL: Mighty Landbreaker - Open a crack in the ground that exposes the aether of the Islands, allows Slayers to gain 3 MIGHT by walking over it. Create one pickup per ammo spent. A Slayer cannot gain this benefit more than once every 45 seconds.
PASSIVE: Frozen Mines - On dodging, create two ice mines that damage any Behemoth that touches them. Recharges every 15 seconds.

The Anvil Gameplay Weapon (Hammer - Frost) x1

Terra rich gauntlets that make the wielder an immovable object. They tether themselves to the Slayer's lifeforce, protecting them and their allies from harm.

LEGENDARY: Oathkeeper's Protection - Gain 500 health, and grant Oathkeeper's Protection to all nearby allies for 15 seconds. When a protected ally would take damage, instead they take no damage, and you take 50% of the damage they would have taken.
SPECIAL: Titanic Bulwark - Smash your fists together, creating a damaging pulse around you, and granting DEFENSE stacks to all nearby allies based on active mantras.
PASSIVE: Reactive Armour - When you take health damage and have no active Shield, gain an equal amount of Shield.

Oathkeepers Gameplay Weapon (Aether Strikers - Terra) x1
